Class StringConditionStrategy

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionHandlerFactory, GrantValidator

    public class StringConditionStrategy
extends AbstractConditionStrategy
    Implementation of string condition strategy, which requires a simple "string" parameter for both granting and checking an entitlement.
